      summary: "CBT rollout in 2025 sped up result turnaround; ~74% passed the Dec 2025 exam.",
      body: "The Philippine Professional Regulation Commission (PRC) Board of Occupational Therapy (under RA 11241, the 2018 Philippine Occupational Therapy Law) shifted its licensure exam to computer-based testing during 2025. December 2025 results were released immediately after the exam (versus the prior 2-working-day turnaround), with 374 of 507 candidates (~74%) passing. The Board's composition rotated between the December 2024 and December 2025 sittings.",
